== Deaths == * Year 2 of {{ill|Kan'ei|ja|寛永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 22|ja|10月22日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1625]] ) – {{ill|Kikkawa Hiroie|ja|吉川広家|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , first lord of {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} in {{ill|Suō Province|ja|Suō Province|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (b. [[1561]] ). * Year 1 of {{ill|Jōō (Edo period)|ja|承応|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 23|ja|10月23日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1652]] ) – {{ill|Betsuki Shōzaemon|ja|別木庄左衛門|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , a masterless samurai (rōnin) (birth year unknown).
