{{Lunisolar September}} '''September 21''' is the 21st day of month {{ill|September (Lunisolar)|ja|9月 (旧暦)|lt=September|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} the 9th month of the traditional {{ill|Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|ja|旧暦|1=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|11=Japanese Lunisolar Calendar|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . It's {{ill|Rokuyō|ja|六曜|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} day is {{ill|Taian|ja|大安|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . == Events == * Year 1 of {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|October 30|ja|10月30日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1673]] ) – Due to the burning of the {{ill|Imperial Palace|ja|内裏|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , floods, and other disasters, the era name changes from {{ill|Kanbun (Japan)|ja|寛文|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} to {{ill|Enpō|ja|延宝|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * Year 7 of {{ill|Kaei|ja|嘉永|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 11|ja|11月11日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1854]] ) – The {{ill|Edo shogunate|ja|幕府|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} orders two steam-powered warships, {{ill|Kanrin Maru|ja|咸臨丸|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and {{ill|Chōyō Maru|ja|朝陽丸|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , from the {{ill|Kingdom of the Netherlands|ja|オランダ|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} . * Year 3 of {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1863]] ) – Farmers in {{ill|Kamo District, Aichi|ja|加茂郡|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , {{ill|Mikawa Province|ja|三河国|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , revolt to demand lower commodity prices, marking the first recorded {{ill|Yonaoshi ikki|ja|世直し一揆|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (social reform riots). * Year 3 of {{ill|Bunkyū|ja|文久|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} (Gregorian calendar {{ill|November 2|ja|11月2日|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} , [[1863]] ) – The {{ill|Tosa Domain|ja|土佐藩|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} arrests {{ill|Takechi Zuizan|ja|武市瑞山|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} and other {{ill|Sonjō faction|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft|12=draft}} members in a large-scale political crackdown.
