from the [[:en:Netherlands|Kingdom of the Netherlands]] . * Year 3 of [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 2|November 2]] , [[1863]] ) – Farmers in [[:en:Kamo District, Gifu|Kamo District, Aichi]] , [[:en:Mikawa Province|Mikawa Province]] , revolt to demand lower commodity prices, marking the first recorded {{ill|Yonaoshi ikki|ja|世直し一揆|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Yonaoshi ikki|qq=}} (social reform riots). * Year 3 of [[:en:Bunkyū|Bunkyū]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:November 2|November 2]] , [[1863]] ) – The [[:en:Tosa Domain|Tosa Domain]] arrests [[:en:Takechi Hanpeita|Takechi Zuizan]] and other {{ill|Sonjō faction|ja|Sonnō jōi faction|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Sonjō faction|qq=}} members in a large-scale political crackdown.
== Births ==
== Deaths == * Year 2 of [[:en:Kan'ei|Kan'ei]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 22|October 22]] , [[1625]] ) – [[:en:Kikkawa Hiroie|Kikkawa Hiroie]] , first lord of {{ill|Iwakuni Domain|ja|岩国領|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Iwakuni Domain|qq=}} in {{ill|Suō Province|ja|Suō Province|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Suō Province|qq=}} (b. [[1561]] ). * Year 1 of [[:en:Jōō (Edo period)|Jōō (Edo period)]] (Gregorian calendar [[:en:October 23|October 23]] , [[1652]] ) – {{ill|Betsuki Shōzaemon|ja|別木庄左衛門|qq=draft|qq=draft|qq=|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Betsuki Shōzaemon|qq=}} , a masterless samurai (rōnin) (birth year unknown).
